uld be observed for a prolonged period following their discontinuation.', 'Synergism', 'Coadministration of chloroquine or hydroxychloroquine with other drugs that can prolong the QT interval should generally be avoided, particularly in patients with baseline QT prolongation (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73898/', '', 'Thiothixene, Lumateperone, Loxapine, Molindone, Cariprazine, Brexpiprazole, Lurasidone', 'Artesunate, Artemether, Pyrimethamine, Tafenoquine, Proguanil, Sulfadoxine', 1767369485);
