, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/73927/', '', 'Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Flunisolide, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Beclomethasone dipropionate, Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Mometasone, Flunisolide, More', 'Asenapine, Pimavanserin, Ziprasidone, Lumateperone, Iloperidone, Amisulpride, Droperidol, Cariprazine, Brexpiprazole, Paliperidone, Lurasidone', 1767369485);
